<pre>
タイトル: <font size = 5>A spirit (StoneBrunt)</font>
<b>投稿者　: </b>Keuzer@Quellious
<!-- ドメイン: 202.219.188.124 -->
URL　　 : <a href="http://village.infoweb.ne.jp/~apfsds/eq">http://village.infoweb.ne.jp/~apfsds/eq</a>
登録時間:2001年9月5日01時40分</pre>
本文:
<center>
<table width="95%">
<tr bgcolor="#000042"><td>
猫村のそばに一匹だけSensetheDeadに反応する赤いWispがいました。<BR>
名前はa spirit。<BR>
<BR>
 You say, 'Hail, a spirit'<BR>
 a spirit flares brightly as you attempt to speak with it. By <BR>
listening very closely you're brely able to make out it's frantic <BR>
whispering. It keep refering to one of the Kejekans, one that <BR>
apparently slew him as he attempted to cleanse the land of them. It <BR>
wants nothing more than to destroy who killed him, but it cannot in <BR>
this [form]. <BR>
 You say, 'what is form'<BR>
 a spirit flares brightly again as it explains there isn't enough <BR>
time for it to explain. It then begins to whisper again, telling you <BR>
that it commands you the aid it in it's revenge. You make out, <BR>
through the barely audible whispering, that if you do help it, you <BR>
will be rewarded. <BR>
 You say, 'what is revenge'<BR>
 a spirit whispers that he will need to become whole again before he <BR>
can defeat the fool animal that slew him. The spirit admits to one <BR>
mistake before coming here to wipe the Kejekans. In an earlier <BR>
campaign, he lost a very powerful weapon. That weapon would enable <BR>
him to take on a form likened to his former self. If you return this <BR>
weapon to the spirit, and then help him to defeat his enemy, the <BR>
reward will be yours. <BR>

